    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <div1 type="letter">
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01800.004_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Elliottstown Effingham Co: Ills:&#8212;<ptr target="loc.04068_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1877-08-11">August 11th /77</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Walt</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Thinking you would like to <choice>
                    <sic>Here</sic>
                    <corr>Hear</corr>
                </choice> from me I would write you a few lines in as much as <choice>
                    <sic>Im</sic>
                    <corr>I'm</corr>
                </choice> well and Hope this will find you the same<ptr target="n0822"/></p>

            <p>Business is very dull Here now and crops is ruined for the want of rain. all of my <choice>
                    <sic>worment</sic>
                    <corr>torment</corr>
                </choice> of of mind and toil of body is of no <choice>
                    <sic>avil</sic>
                    <corr>avail</corr>
                </choice>
                <choice>
                    <sic>Im</sic>
                    <corr>I'm</corr>
                </choice>
                <choice>
                    <sic>feafuly</sic>
                    <corr>fearfully</corr>
                </choice> in want now and when my crops is <choice>
                    <sic>geathered</sic>
                    <corr>gathered</corr>
                </choice> it <choice><sic>wont</sic><corr>won't</corr></choice> be much better as I see
                <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.01800.003_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                O I <choice>
                    <sic>musent</sic>
                    <corr>mustn't</corr>
                </choice> say <choice>
                    <sic>Im</sic>
                    <corr>I'm</corr>
                </choice> in want Because I Have got plenty to eat and some <choice>
                    <sic>close</sic>
                    <corr>clothes</corr>
                </choice></p>

            <p>But not much money now I <choice>
                    <sic>dont</sic>
                    <corr>don't</corr>
                </choice>
                <choice>
                    <sic>nead</sic>
                    <corr>need</corr>
                </choice> as much</p>

            <p>But the <choice>
                    <sic>fuather</sic>
                    <corr>future</corr>
                </choice> looks dark But may come out Better than
                I <choice>
                    <sic>amagn</sic>
                    <corr>imagine</corr>
                </choice></p>

            <p>I will Buy some Hogs on a credit and feed my <choice>
                    <sic>unsailable</sic>
                    <corr>unsellable</corr>
                </choice> corn to them and may come out all right in due time I received those papers many thanks)</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>yours truly</salute>
                <signed>Jos. C. Baldwin</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript><p>write soon</p></postscript></div1>
